  icon: {fileID: 21300000, guid: fbfb192cd7dfe0e4eb7fe112ecc7d972, type: 3}
  text: You come by a shady figure, lugging around a huge sack. The bag oozes purple
    at the seems. He looks towards you, and offers his wares.
  choices:
  - text: Take the mottled arm.
    subtext: Pay 3 Kaltos, Gain Yellow Card, Take 3 Damage
    effect: {fileID: 11400000, guid: c01c6b3cc6eb7964bb9aabf2edce0ea1, type: 2}
  - text: Take the tentacled chest wrap.
    subtext: Pay 3 Kaltos, Gain Green Card, Take 3 Damage
    effect: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 1d38794949b9d184e877a0a8ad048bbe, type: 2}
  - text: Take the dripping knee cap.
    subtext: Pay 3 Kaltos, gain Purple Card, Take 3 Damage
    effect: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 784fd461d0120394c8ce72d9ffd5db68, type: 2}
  - text: Ignore her.
    subtext: 
    effect: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 777e0b881c1878948b602d5cc7afc494, type: 2}
